      ”Bioinformatics : The machine learning approach” 2nd Edition
       MIT Press
[T2] A.D. Baxevanis, B.F.F. Quellette
      “Bioinformatics: A Practical guide to the analysis of genes and proteins” 3rd Edition
       Wiley-Interscience

